# Points Transfer [(by GoWMan)](https://www.twitch.tv/gowman)

## Description
Use this system to transfer points from Streamelements or Streamlabs to Streamer.bot using the [Points System (by VRFlad)](/en/extensions/points-system/points-system-core).

## Installation

This setup allows an easy way to transfer points from Streamelements or Streamlabs to Streamer.bot without any complicated maintenence and should allow for a one and done setup.

Copy the text from the code box below into the `Import` box in Streamer.bot to add these to your action library:

```text

```
![points-system-points-transfer-import.png](/extensions/points-system/images/points-system-points-transfer-import.png)

## Configuration

For Streamelements points [Streamelements-CSV](https://github.com/Slikrick/streamelements-csv) is needed to export points to a CSV file.

For Streamlabs click on connections in the bottom left corner. Next click on cloud and then click Export Currency CSV and save the CSV file on a local readable drive.
![points-system-stream-labs-chat-bot.png](/extensions/points-system/images/points-system-stream-labs-chat-bot.png)
